诊者，拥有消极情绪的青少年范围可能更广，一些量表调查显示，2020 年，中国青少年抑郁检出率达 24.6％，而乡村儿童的抑郁检出率为 25.2％。 当孩子从学校掉队，甚至想放弃生命时，越来越多家长意识到孩子可能是生病了，而不是「矫情」。当孩子被确诊后，总希望医生解答「为什么」。面对这些急切的询问，何凡很难给出简单又确定的答案。她向《中国新闻周刊》承认，在青少年的诸多心理问题中，抑郁和焦虑受社会文化环境因素影响更大，但并不能简单归因于某个因素。「抑郁症是时代病，我们的家庭、学校和社会组成的生态系统出了问题」。儿童精神科挤满了抑郁症小患者，这届孩子为什么这么「烦」？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e081fda494fb53f097a97d85d434b6b7_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/505080433"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4PjKjrbOvsJTEAMaCDc0NTIxMjQwIMv+y40GMAk47AFALXIJNTA1MDgwNDMzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1639382608.3385446", "card_id": "Q_502885560", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 42}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2022 年有哪些值得跨年特意去玩的城市？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-bc9397a97cb14c24bd0c9ac56ca1d0e8_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/502885560"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I4PjKjrbOvsJTEAMaCDc0MDMzNTQwIJr1m40GMAA4S0Aucgk1MDI4ODU1NjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1639382608.3389413", "card_id": "Q_317906851", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "该怎么为人处世？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-386d18869bb47f415585efb535a2f001_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/317906851"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4PjKjrbOvsJTEAMaCDMyOTIyMzA1IOiT9OQFMAI4hAJAL3IJMzE3OTA2ODUxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "